snippet.title: Ultimate Spider-Man - Walkthrough Part 1 - Chapter 1: Father's Pride (Spider-Man Vs. Venom)
snippet.description:
Ultimate Spider-Man - Walkthrough Part 1 - Chapter 1: Father's Pride (Spider-Man Vs. Venom)

Walkthrough of Ultimate Spider-Man in High Definition on the PlayStation 2.

Follow me on Twitter for the latest updates and walkthroughs: https://twitter.com/#!/Banish21

Release Date: September 22, 2005

Systems: Microsoft Windows, Xbox, Nintendo DS, PlayStation 2, Gamecube, Nintendo DS, Gameboy Advance, 

Developer: Vicarious Visions, Beenox, Treyarch,

Publisher: Activision

Description: 

Based on the comic book of the same name, Ultimate Spider-Man lets you play as either the hero Spider-Man or his arch-nemesis, Venom. Use the unique combat techniques of either Spider-Man or Venom to battle a host of Spider-Man characters. Artistic contributions by the creators of the series make for an authentic Spider-Man experience.
